{"tid":2404234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上瘋傳屋邨保安唔畀收利是 網民：世界末日喇","createTime":"2021-02-11T14:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T16:21:33.000Z","uid":100150,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77188919358e8d6a3bb72a3bc8ba00873125efee","tid":2404234,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/dc6929c8d64d882e5d4149880e9cdff8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210211/_2021021116403053345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fdc6929c8d64d882e5d4149880e9cdff8%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210211%2F_2021021116403053345.jpg&h=9b317ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每逢農曆新年，不少保安員都會非常期待「𢭃利是」這個環節。不過，網上近日就瘋傳一張屋邨通告，當中列明保安員不可以收利是！<br />\n<br />\n網上近日流傳一張房屋協會的通告，當中寫明房協屬下員工受《防止賄賂條例》約束，不可以收受任何利益，包括利是或禮物；而根據合約條款，房協所聘請的服務承辦商及其僱員（包括保安員、清潔及保養承辦商員工）亦然。<br />\n<br />\n一眾網民看後都紛紛表示這是「保安員的世界末日」，並為保安員抱不平，「新年派利是乃中國人的習俗，取其意頭，大家利利是是而已，小小意思算什麼貪污？」亦有不少網民搞笑回應指「邊個話利是入面一定係『利益』，我畀張紅紙畀保安唔係唔得下化」、「過年咪冇保安返工」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1997949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1997949&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=86a12615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1997949&h=a9e16bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1997949</a>"},{"pid":"45a02d92149067f97cc0c5eb306d652f0c089610","tid":2404234,"uid":28397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"獄卒收嘅係死囚家屬嘅賄賂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df17de4ae3dc8d7741e4d09b43e70ebd0221815","tid":2404234,"ui